Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] What kind of\Nrestaurant is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if... if...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...this were a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, he's escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Krieg's henchman\Nattacked us and vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--[FULLBODY] He what?\N--[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... This is a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, but how will you be\Npaying for your meal today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will a bullet be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have\Nany money then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just found my cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NSanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI sighs]\NStupid geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an opportunity\Nyou don't want to pass up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need to keep you\Nhere at my restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "The Strongest Pirate\NFleet! Commodore Don Krieg!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, pal...\NI'm the Sous Chef in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you\Ndon't need me any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight with customers\Nall the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You flirt with every woman under\N80 who walks through here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even cook\Na decent meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worth less to me than\Nthe chum after brunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NOh, and let's not forget about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,how the other cooks avoid\Nyou like you were poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So just run off and be\Na pirate or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but get out of this restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You shoot off at the mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and expect that I'm just\Ngoing to take it, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I could blow\Noff everything you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't listen to\Nanyone trash my cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying here as a\NSous Chef, and that's final!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NWhat do you think you're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,grabbing your boss\Nby the collar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZEFF] You ingrate!\N--[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--[wood, glass shatters]\N--[CUSTOMERS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]\NDumb... geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NEnough with the games...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try to kick me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm here to stay. I'm not\Ngoing anywhere, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not till you're dead and gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NDead? Hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got another hundred years\Nof kickin' your ass left in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] He's always\Ngotta have the last word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He said it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can make it up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with this delightful fruit\NMacedonia, my princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're too kind!\NIt looks wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't forget about\Nus, Mister Casanova!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better get some\Nkind of an apology, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This tea should be more\Nthan adequate for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you should\Nbe thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him out, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYou take him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please don't\Nfight because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, my dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said it was about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That all of the food\Nhere is just delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a little\Ntoo expensive for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI] Oh! Thank you!\N--[SANJI stammering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys still\Ngotta pay, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHow very generous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] What are you\Nsitting around for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not here\Nto lounge around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NRight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sighs]\NWe've been sitting around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,twiddling our thumbs\Nfor four days now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you think we're\Ngonna be here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll stay a year,\Nbut I'm already so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit whining,\Nthis place is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, all the food here is free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYeah, for you it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we still doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's just\Nget outta this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit tight a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna try to make\Nanother deal with the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NUgh, well, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling? Hey, What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER A gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER A screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER B]\NIt's them... They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hourglasses\Nmean our time is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That flag means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt; it belongs\Nto the ruler of the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER C] But why? Why have\Nthe Krieg Pirates come here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! I knew those\Ngoons would show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now are you gonna get rid\Nof those guys or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real! He's got\Na whole fleet to command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Don Krieg come here to\Nget revenge for just one man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, doesn't he have\Nanything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here, all right! We're not\Nimagining that ship, are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, don't panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think this is our\Ncue to leave, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the sheer\Nsize of that galleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a huge ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Ghin came back to\Nrepay you for your kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously doubt that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's something else.\N--[LUFFY] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Their ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what'd they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sail through a hurricane\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like damage\Ninflicted by cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it doesn't\Nlook man-made at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Hmm, then maybe\Nit was a tornado-hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThere he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--[footsteps]\N--[CUSTOMERS gasp, whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I need food... and water...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long, I don't even\Nremember the last time I ate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--I need food and drink...\N--[GHIN groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the death\Nand destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the Don Krieg,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore of the\Ngrand pirate fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Guess he's hungry.\N--[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NC-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help him! Our captain\Nis on the brink of starvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had a single\Nbite to eat for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll die if he doesn't\Nget some food soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY laughs]\NThis is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't laughed that\Nhard in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Don Krieg,\Nkneeling before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here as\Ncustomers this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\NI'm that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get a hold of\Nthe marines right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finally weak\Nenough to be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This may never happen again,\Nand I'm not gonna ruin it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,by helping him get\Nhis strength back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER A]\NHe's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what he'll do if\Ngets on his feet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER D]\NHe's done terrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER E] And as soon as he's\Nup, he'll keep on doin' 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we let him starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he's back to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll kill every last\Nperson in this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't get so much as\Na glass of water from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI won't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI won't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll leave quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...\NBe merciful, and help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a king,\NDon Krieg, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't reduce\Nyourself to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better than\Nthe common beggar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir! What\Nabout your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... I'll take the scraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN sobs]\NDon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, boo-hoo for\Nthe cruel pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHey, step aside, Patty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NSanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Here's something\Nfor your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that food away\Nfrom him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize he's a cold,\Nheartless, killing machine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man known as\Nthe ruler of the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the most treacherous\Nof all pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started back in prison...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He pretended to be a Marine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he decided to\Ndeclare his pirate ambitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he took command\Nof a Marine vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,by killing the senior officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE] He would raise the\NMarine flag to enter ports,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then lay waste to the\Nunsuspecting cities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and passenger ships there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He even showed the white flag\Nbefore attacking enemy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He did anything\Nto secure victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy fights dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE] He's also unmatched\Nin physical combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he'll\Njust leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible with a\Nbloodthirsty killer like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He deserves death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG sneers]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not what we agreed on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me your word! I only\Nbrought you here because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you promised that you\Nwouldn't ruin this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or hurt the man who saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYes, that was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--[bones cracking]\N--[GHIN screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMERS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey... You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is\Ngoing on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know. Let's\Ngo inside and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure am. You sound scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NIt's so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship looks almost abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty good ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can all see,\Nmy ship is a wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I'll be\Nneeding a nice new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After a few small chores...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every last one of you\Nwill leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg...\NYou promised... Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThere are about a hundred men
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,left onboard my ship,\Nall are weak with hunger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and many are seriously wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your lives, you\Nwill prepare food and water
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for every last one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost too many\Nmen to hunger already...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B groaning]\NWater...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NBring them over immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling us to\Nfeed our executioners?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear how stupid\Nthat sounds?! We refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now make no mistake,\Nyou wretched cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not placing an order...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am giving you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I make myself clear?!\NDon't defy me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NSanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean for\Nthis to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you brought on this\Nrestaurant, you stupid bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think\Nyou're going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NTo the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll be cooking\Na hundred more meals today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN, LUFFY]\NSanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN, LUFFY]\NSanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NWhat?! Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... Hop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the truth, Sanji!\NAre you his spy or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you go\Nanywhere near that kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] We're fed up\Nwith you acting insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NAll right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NStop me if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NI know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no secret that Don Krieg\Nis a terrible, ruthless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NBut that doesn't matter to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NIt doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After we feed all these men, who\Nknows what's going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just a simple cook,\Nno more and no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone's going hungry,\Nit's my duty to feed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Somebody grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NYou bring free food to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the bums I kick outta this\Nplace, over and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not about to\Nargue over who's right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in that particular situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time, you're just\Nflat out wrong, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you do things\Nlike that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to\Nprotect this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, we've got\Nnumbers on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Don Krieg, but what\Ncould he do against all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At a joint like this, pirate\Nscumbags come and go all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fully prepared to\Nserve any kind of customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope you saved\Nsome room for dessert...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...'cause I have\Na secret recipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...that is truly to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Open wide! Here comes\Nthe Meat Ball of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN, LUFFY gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NI might've broken the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope Zeff doesn't\Nyell at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NHe might go easy on you for
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,saving the restaurant and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we going\Nto do about all the guys
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,left in Krieg's ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fry 'em! Cover it in batter,\Nand fry the entire thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, NAMI gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NAre you a chef or a comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your jokes are lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NAnd that dessert was terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst I ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp, scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NSo die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got 'em everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All those guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You cooks should\Nnot have defied me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am by far the\Nworld's strongest man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Arms, made of solid steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wootz steel body\Narmor, impenetrable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And a diamond fist that could\Npound this entire world to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to the\Nweapons on my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a fleet of 50 ships\Nwith five thousand pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My record is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won every single battle\Nthat I've ever been in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the only one\Nfit to be called Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NOutta the way, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-- Uh! [groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give you\Nslime balls an order,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you will follow it\Ndown to the last letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever disobey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about a hundred meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take it to your\Nmen right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NNo, Owner Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're\Ngoing with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was standing there, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Red Foot Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Think it's okay to\Ngive Krieg food like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.49,0:24:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Yeah, do something\Nabout that, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI will. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.62,0:24:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Hey! Where are\Nyou off to, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.29,0:24:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Don't go picking a\Nfight with Krieg, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NA fight, huh? Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You fightin', Luffy?\NNeed a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.83,0:24:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.63,0:24:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Protect Baratie! The Great\NPirate, Red Foot Zeff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.34,0:24:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates!

